{"tid":2506433,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"遼寧艦失去動力被拖回港？台灣媒體/CCTOY又造謠了","createTime":"2021-04-27T10:09:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T10:18:32.000Z","uid":391580,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"97bd61ff0cbe22b61a6038fb98886fd843b866d8","tid":2506433,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXhthMm9GQEZ6bmYnbN7YTXmZW4e9XD5e8hPESJxGiiW9?filename=eqFCq59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeqFCq59.jpg&h=4df9be0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今天，台灣親綠媒體《自由時報》刊登了一條&ldquo;解放軍遼寧艦失去動力被拖回港&rdquo;的新聞，還配上了戲謔的導語，讓島內不少網民極為興奮跳腳。可筆者查閱了新聞內文和素材發現，台媒這次的造謠水准實在讓人哭笑不得。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZBRfKeQ3fKqYzKhhoVc61uB9kZJ5wGQ7uxPjiyrfiUHQ?filename=pdvF8it.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpdvF8it.jpg&h=27ef2ab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點進這篇報道的正文，&ldquo;遼寧艦失去動力&rdquo;這一說法的消息來源被表述為&ldquo;網傳&rdquo;。從台媒給出的鏈接看，這個&ldquo;網&rdquo;還不是什麼專業機構，而是島內日常閑聊的論壇&ldquo;批踢踢實業坊&rdquo;（PTT）。<br />\n<br />\n把論壇作為消息來源就夠離譜了，更離譜的是，這個來源就是一張配了幾行文字的圖片，消息稱&ldquo;遼寧艦半道失去動力，以極低速行駛&rdquo;。至于這場&ldquo;事故&rdquo;發生的時間、地點，以及消息原始發布者的信息，上面一概沒有。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTa6wMTqFmEjpYz6ih4wbjtZJhB2wsmmbtLf19BEXqL1y?filename=gjujEqm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgjujEqm.jpg&h=5235bb09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在發布到Facebook平台時，《自由時報》的編輯還給此新聞配上了&ldquo;就算不能成為世界塞子，也要成為世界亮點&rdquo;的轉發導語，帶着一大群島內網民一起大肆嘲諷解放軍航母&ldquo;熄火&rdquo;。不少留言笑稱&ldquo;這種實力還想武統台灣&rdquo;、&ldquo;丟人丟到極點&rdquo;。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmR5nvrVAi4hiQAuQpgLjUE9ymFvP1KvcDbFdBfwy4VWhG?filename=4VMaL5t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4VMaL5t.jpg&h=b90795e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只不過，沒多久就有網友找到了那個所謂&ldquo;消息源&rdquo;的出處，這則消息最早由一個網名叫&ldquo;Fisher Yu&rdquo;的賬號發布，在這則消息結尾，原文還有一個&ldquo;狗頭&rdquo;表情包。在中文網絡裏，&ldquo;加狗頭&rdquo;有故意說反話&ldquo;釣魚&rdquo;的內涵，再加上這個博主的網名叫&ldquo;Fisher&rdquo;（漁夫）的意思，這就讓人不免懷疑，他發布這一消息是在故意逗某些盼着大陸和解放軍倒黴的人了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfT4LtEU1NaxHewUV1QSDqghMSH2JooAkio9Ri4sLVubp?filename=9ddHCcg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ddHCcg.jpg&h=13e6b859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對于日常造謠的某些台媒來說，為了政治目的引用不可靠消息源可謂家常便飯，被網友忽悠釣魚也不是第一次了。但《自由時報》這次造謠還是玩出了一些新花樣的。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">點進他們這則消息的正文可以看到，他們自己在文中還提到，有越南軍事記者發布了一張&ldquo;遼寧艦行程衛星圖&rdquo;，給出了疑似遼寧艦的行駛軌迹，沒有任何迹象能證明遼寧艦出現了所謂&ldquo;接近熄火&rdquo;的問題。</span></span><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">《自由時報》在文中也承認，遼寧艦目前很可能正航向巴士海峽，所謂&ldquo;熄火&rdquo;的傳言並不靠譜。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWB3rNrYBVm5GimQjSK1zKdEdDp2TpGgfLEti2uaozSs1?filename=VDpPhcq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVDpPhcq.jpg&h=6c93fbf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此外，據公開資料顯示，在4月23日人民海軍成立72周年前夕，遼寧艦還和多艘解放軍戰艦在台灣周邊海域進行訓練，《自由時報》在此前也對此進行了報道。那麼，為什麼他們明知道所謂的&ldquo;網傳&rdquo;是謠言，還要這麼激動地大肆報道呢？這個恐怕只有他們自己清楚了。<br />\n<br />\n至于《自由時報》導語說的&ldquo;世界塞子&rdquo;、&ldquo;世界亮點&rdquo;，如果我們沒記錯的話，真正塞住蘇伊士運河，給全世界航運惹了大麻煩，還被島內沾沾自喜當做&ldquo;被全世界關注&rdquo;的亮點的，恰恰是台灣自己的艦船。<br />\n<br />\n就是請《自由時報》在造謠之余不要忘了，台灣那艘&ldquo;長賜號&rdquo;還因為沒有繳清罰款，被扣在蘇伊士運河呢。"},{"pid":"2ee2a2519974db3a7237fc96652467642a06bc3e","tid":2506433,"uid":374180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:12:12.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2506433\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2506433</a>"},{"pid":"e7189995a03df7d3abf7d7cd5a94711147803e38","tid":2506433,"uid":25612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:12:15.000Z","msg":"你幫敵人澄清算唔算投敵？"},{"pid":"f202fad5a30ba394c9dd6e8f90843ebcec9bb21f","tid":2506433,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7189995a03df7d3abf7d7cd5a94711147803e38","tid":2506433,"uid":25612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:12:15.000Z","msg":"你幫敵人澄清算唔算投敵？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:12:54.000Z","msg":"兒登仔笑死人，睇住台灣ptt嘅假新聞喺度打飛機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2504321\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2504321</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1cf1cd9b291e22238209011eceaf4f249d0eff37","tid":2506433,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7189995a03df7d3abf7d7cd5a94711147803e38","tid":2506433,"uid":25612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:12:15.000Z","msg":"你幫敵人澄清算唔算投敵？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:13:05.000Z","msg":"唔通由得自己人炒車?"},{"pid":"77579733b6ea8495d1b58c76285b4bf74b5f730c","tid":2506433,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cf1cd9b291e22238209011eceaf4f249d0eff37","tid":2506433,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7189995a03df7d3abf7d7cd5a94711147803e38","tid":2506433,"uid":25612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:12:15.000Z","msg":"你幫敵人澄清算唔算投敵？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:13:05.000Z","msg":"唔通由得自己人炒車?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:13:49.000Z","msg":"我喺佢哋話遼寧艦死火個post入面笑佢哋仲畀人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e9e8b6f6233c484b40d175eb06462f3d9800d5","tid":2506433,"uid":310446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:16:19.000Z","msg":"架嘢死火又係誇張咗嘅<br />\n不過一路俾人影低哂行蹤都唔係好得去邊<br />\n說好的隱形呢？"},{"pid":"72a530c89bdb5606c1507d0c5a43f963f75af52c","tid":2506433,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:17:09.000Z","msg":"兒登仔又話死火，屌<br />\n<br />\n26號最新新聞中美船隻仲喺度互相追逐緊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmR6F8GmPfLqqmKuj7Cmx4r9oJR5cdyLqX7jegUpgk96z7?filename=QzNdJVa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQzNdJVa.jpg&h=c2df0a75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2281265f10ab56fc1884e560e53f73766589e258","ti